## Devil's Advocate Review for Plan [PLAN_NUMBER]

### 0. Plan Status Verification (MANDATORY - Do This First)

Before any other analysis, verify the plan actually needs implementation:

| Check | Result | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| [ ] Execution steps in plan file: All unchecked? | Yes/No | If checked, plan may be complete |
| [ ] workflow_state.md: Plan listed as COMPLETE? | Yes/No | Trust workflow_state if conflict |
| [ ] Code existence: Files in File Impact Map exist? | Yes/No | If yes, work may be done |
| [ ] Supersession: Any related plan marked SUPERSEDED? | Yes/No | Check for overlapping plans |

**If any verification fails, STOP and clarify status before proceeding with review.**

